#: patterns/faq/accordion-sidebar.php:51
#: patterns/faq/default.php:39
msgid "This layout is the default Home template. To replace it with your own content, simply create a new Page, publish it, and assign it as your \"Homepage\" under Settings → Reading. Once your new Homepage is set, you should delete the front-page.php template file from the theme to prevent it from overriding your chosen page."
