#: patterns/page/home.php:1724
msgid "How do I change fonts and colors globally?"
msgstr ""

#: patterns/faq/accordion.php:77
#: patterns/page/home.php:1726
msgid "Open the Styles panel (the half-shaded circle icon) in the top-right of the Editor. Changes made here propagate instantly across the entire site architecture, updating all blocks simultaneously."
