#: patterns/page/home.php:1734
msgid "How do I add custom SVG images?"
msgstr ""

#: patterns/faq/accordion.php:86
#: patterns/page/home.php:1736
msgid "Use the Icon Block to manage curated sets or the Inline SVG variation to paste raw XML code directly onto the canvas."
