#: patterns/page/home.php:1792
msgid "How do I edit the Header or Footer?"
msgstr ""

#: patterns/faq/default.php:115
#: patterns/page/home.php:1794
msgid "These are Template Parts. You can edit them contextually while viewing any template in the Editor, or manage them specifically under Appearance → Editor → Patterns."
msgstr ""

